          }}></path></svg></a>{`Change the time or timezone of Hummingbot`}</h3>
    <p>{`Hummingbot follows the same date/time and timezone on the machine where it is intalled. Below are some steps you can follow to change the timezone depending on the operating system and installation type.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Docker`}</strong></p>
    <p>{`While docker `}<code parentName="p" {...{
        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`$instance_name`}</code>{` is running in the background, type in the command line.`}</p>
    <div {...{
      "className": "gatsby-highlight",
      "data-language": "text"
    }}><pre parentName="div" {...{
        "style": {
          "counterReset": "linenumber NaN"
        },
        "className": "language-text line-numbers"
      }}><code parentName="pre" {...{
          "className": "language-text"
        }}>{`#Run this command
docker exec -u 0 -it instance_name bash

#Install tzdata for the instance/container
apt-get update && apt-get install -y tzdata

#Run this command to change the docker timezone
dpkg-reconfigure tzdata`}</code><span parentName="pre" {...{
          "aria-hidden": "true",
          "className": "line-numbers-rows",
          "style": {
            "whiteSpace": "normal",
            "width": "auto",
            "left": "0"
          }
        }}><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span><span parentName="span"></span></span></pre></div>
    <p>{`Configure geographic location and timezone by inputting the corresponding number, see example below:`}</p>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "/1b06e86aa7724d2b50eabb864fd30e34/time-zone.png",
        "alt": null
      }}></img></p>
    <p>{`Restart your docker and start your Hummingbot again to apply changes.`}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Windows`}</strong></p>
    <p>{`You can change the timezone on a Windows computer by doing the following:`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`Press `}<strong parentName="p">{`Win + R`}</strong>{` shortcut to open the Run dialog box`}</p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`Enter `}<strong parentName="p">{`timedate.cpl`}</strong>{` to open Date and Time settings`}</p>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`Click `}<strong parentName="p">{`Change time zone`}</strong></p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "/6761208969659416493ac5970ab7542f/win-time.png",
        "alt": null
      }}></img></p>
    <p>{`You can also follow these steps in the Windows Support article: `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/how-to-set-your-time-and-time-zone-dfaa7122-479f-5b98-2a7b-fa0b6e01b261"
      }}>{`How to set your time and timezone`}</a></p>
