    <p>{`If you're stuck in the terminal window where you attempt to open or create a new instance for Hummingbot, there might already be a malfunction that causes the software/application to freeze or crash.`}</p>
    <p><img parentName="p" {...{
        "src": "/4b31be20fb2a233c7c63025d2ef5cbd0/docker-ps-a.png",
        "alt": null
      }}></img></p>
